Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reaction called "consequence" awaits you whenever an action is taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch's power could not change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he has the power to enforce absolute obedience to any order he gives,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is unable to escape from the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch acted in order to avenge his mother and turn the world into a place where his sister, Nunnally, can live happily in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you see, the world and the people keep threatening him with a "consequence" different from what he imagined,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they continue to hunt for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that "continuation" were to spread throughout the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where is the one who will bear the sins and take the punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders to 401: Repel the enemy as you move, heading towards 9 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, rendezvous with the main force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pursue it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, protecting the Governor-General comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Ougi? It's me, C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't move right now, but he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issue the order to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be completely annihilated if we drag this out any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you to be so shocked that you couldn't even-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My gun is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone took it while I was unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone saw your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were at least two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One who fired, and one who was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing to Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to meet Her Highness Princess Euphemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank... I want to thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She protected Nina with her life during the Hoteljacking incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She stood up and identified herself as Euphemia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she {\i1}is{\i0} a princess! If I were to hook up with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that people with such impure thoughts would be able to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Impure"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally-chan is so harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she, Miss President?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I let Lelouch act up around me doesn't mean that I want you doing it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to meet Princess Euphemia too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-san, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's someone who is very high above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? This is the Ashford Academy Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there... anything unusual happening there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley has yet to show up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, you've been absent from class. You should behave more like a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, Mr. Model Student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell Nunnally that I'll be coming home late tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really "coming home late", it's "coming home late again", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of being in the same school if you never see each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arthur, argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he fooling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It seems that Suzaku doesn't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that, I suppose the thread connecting the witness to the army has been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than the army and the Order of the Black Knights,\NI don't think anyone else would have been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is also a chance a survivor from the Japanese Liberation Army saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they only stole a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Ougi to investigate the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've collected it, but it will take time to analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I saw Shirley on that battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the girl who kissed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just checking, you horny little punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you really saw her, we should investigate this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it this operation or the one at the Narita Mountain Range,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's obvious they are targeting you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very normal to target the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was the incident with His Highness Prince Clovis as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, rather than being an enemy to Britannia as a whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is possibly acting in order to take revenge upon the Britannian Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia, did you stand up to save the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are still the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let something like the Hoteljacking incident happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about arranging a knight for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we dedicate a knight to protecting Princess Euphemia,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she can form her own personal unit using this person as the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:07:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia has the right to do so since she is the Vice Governor-General.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought he was truly a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think his reaction towards human lives is a little abnormal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no abnormalities were seen in the data from the actual combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I was thinking of testing {\i1}that{\i0}.{probably the impulse silhouette/strike aile rip off pack -_-}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in the middle of making adjustments to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, stop treating Suzaku-kun as a part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't see your point,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you won't be able to convey your thoughts if you don't communicate with him properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you treating him like a replacement for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm~ :>?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only tend to notice strange things, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I {\i1}am{\i0} your superior after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for my room to be disinfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I search through other people's underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me big time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would go faster if you did it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the man who that woman loves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being held down by weird things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the gun couldn't be found anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her diary is only updated until the 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 14th?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the day her father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pictures of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she a lovely suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narita?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a majestic memorial, Shirley Fenette-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame. Just a bit more, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take down that white armor next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Tamaki was defeated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship of the Liberation Front...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They self-destructed, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They contacted us asking for help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Zero act because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a chance to see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you still doubt Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing was too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan on doing if Zero was really behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to imply?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Diethard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you ran away in fear earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Britannian weaklings don't have the right to question us, the Executive Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was assigned only to assess the battle's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had Ougi-san's approval too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero said he didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like her? That girl named Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you going to Narita?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously because she may have found out my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do after you find out? Eliminate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put in too much effort into it if it's something you don't really want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... from experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch is such a cruel man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know about Lulu too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were tricked by him, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mouth gave the order to kill your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stole away your kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't forgive those kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both you and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rather surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student himself is Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's a Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hand him over to Governor-General Cornelia, I can become a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just a dame, but a real noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great. I wonder what kind of punishment awaits you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for you, the Governor-General would...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he your boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have committed the same crime as Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but you also made use of the death of your father in order to gain compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A manipulative woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You acted pitiful on purpose because you wanted him to be nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the sympathetic look make you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to play the part of a tragic heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought about those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who killed someone and seduced a man, are not fit to be a heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the wicked witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that Lelouch likes some other woman, but you still hung around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:31.47,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you post a screenshot of this onto 4ch saying "fansubbers = stupid", please read: http://www.snopes.com/language/notthink/deserts.htm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for you to get your just deserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embrace this emotion for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embrace it all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't bear your sins and set your heart free,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you and Lelouch will be terribly pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this would be the place, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we have no choice but to split up and look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what she looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chances are low. She shouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are going to do after you find out? Eliminate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person and Shirley...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Once again from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Shirley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, isn't that nice? What a scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A face that shows that you won't forgive me for striking your woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHERE IS SHIRLEY?!{WHERE IS SARAH CONNOR?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:03.48,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Batuan is a style of painting originating from Bali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any photos. As for pictures, I can draw in the Batuan style...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break. Do you expect me to wait until you finish drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's faster for you to ask the army or the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be caught in a boring pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you start looking from the high ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Lelouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it him? The other witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chess game is most likely a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably aims to lure me to a deserted place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've played this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was calling my cell phone a pretense?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's because he doesn't know what I look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he didn't have time to take a photo of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he wasn't preparing the area for a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make use of flaws to break through?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you pay more attention to the duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar. What was that about this being the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, unless it's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, because it's you, you can't win against Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it okay if we consider this my victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated me completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear about me from C.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came up with fourteen possibilities of my true identity in just a brief moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one of those is right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Geass user?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. Your Geass is useless unless you're in direct contact with your target's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about those rules too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read my mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of Geass I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you shoot Shirley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...! You shot Shirley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we start the punishment game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't your usual self yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, that gun is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's Zero's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu's gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have yet to use it on her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can fire at you immediately if you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he only read surface thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there restrictions to his Geass usage like mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time level, a duration?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are his intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he intends to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it through and use the strategies you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin, spin, spin around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more suitable than death for someone who fools with the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'll die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She fired at another witness in order to protect your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that blood stain was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu, let's end it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. Sins need to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, you made Shirley...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can read a person's mind, he can easily control and mislead them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, don't be fooled by him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. The one who lied to her is you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If killing is a sin, then don't sin again by killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid! You know just what to say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really kill someone? Aren't you just being misled by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She figured it out herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it's meaningless to continue to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That couldn't happen! Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one who killed your father, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him, he's just a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her thoughts are in a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. I get it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the two of you to sort it out by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? To think I made it so dramatic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's boring, I'll make the two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I didn't notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really you! I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mao. You did it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C.C., that dress is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C.C., I'll come to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely! Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mao...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you actually came out from the heart of a person....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, you're not at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu, I shot you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Lulu, I shot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive it, your sin. I'll bear all of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to be kind to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Father died...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. It's okay if you want to forget all of the horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you forget everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, I'm sorry about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If reincarnation exists, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, did you lose a family member too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not a family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a precious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only realized it for the first time, after losing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how often her smile saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer argue or laugh like that together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I didn't know what I came here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I came to put an end to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:22:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there are a lot of things you can't forget, and a lot of sad things too,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the morning will still come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no need to overdo it by bearing them in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:23:58.98,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I might have been naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:02.25,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been better if I had eliminated Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.61,0:24:03.04,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:05.67,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Geass...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:08.52,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,If this power causes people to be lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:11.05,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have a soul that is able to endure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:12.68,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Mao...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.07,0:24:14.36,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,my vengeance!
